{
  "stem": "17761.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 122.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember my father was reading from the Torah.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he was also Hattan Torah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And to see him again these-- all these people around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was no institution, no nothing, no community, no link, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Years later in my synagogue in Israel, I got to be [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This Sefer Torah is actually in my synagogue in Israel.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's a long story.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I asked that [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I should read it in that Sefer Torah.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I made a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Have As I just start to read [NON-ENGLISH], I saw my father there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And I couldn't utter a single word.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The community didn't know anything about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'm going to stop the tape now.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I started to read, as I said.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was just impossible for me to read.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I started to cry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every word was just as difficult as to cross the-- the Red Sea.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody understood what was going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody thought that I am so moved by the fact that they gave me the honor of being Hattan Torah and therefore I was crying.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And slowly, slowly I finished reading.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I had no problems with [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then my wife and me, we gave a big kiddush in the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that is as usual, the Hattan Torah has to say [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And naturally, I prepared something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But then I said to the entire congregation, my dear friends, this time I won't say any [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I'm going to tell you the story about the Torah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And for the first time I told the story to my congregation.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Until nowadays, it's a matter of about 20 years ago.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They still remember the story with that Torah.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
